Standards-Version: 4.2.1

Package: braille-translator
Architecture: all
Depends: ${python3:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, python3-louis, python3-gi, gir1.2-gtk-3.0
Description: Graphical user interface for Braille translation using Liblouis
 Braille-Translator facilitate translating text to braille. Additionally, it 
 offers features such as line cutting, select and translate,
 back translation, and exporting in a Braille Ready Format (BRF) 
 .
 It supports several braille tables thanks to liblouis.
